<h1 id="lombardpress-diplomatic-transcription-guidelines">LombardPress Diplomatic Transcription Guidelines</h1>

<p>Editors:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Jeffrey C. Witt (Loyola University Maryland)</li>
  <li>Michael Stenskj√¶r Christensen (University of Copenhagen)</li>
